            <lg xml:id="TK1197">
<l>paruvaralum paitaluṅ kāṇāṉkol kāma </l>
<l> ṉoruvarka ṇiṉṟoḻuku vāṉ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Would not cupid who abides and contends in one party (only) witness the pain and sorrow (in that party)?</l>
